app_name: Groups Treatment Groups Apple Translate Daily Translator Learn Speak
app_description: Daily translator is an excellent translation app that is not only comparable to the native translation software on your iPhone but also brings a richer experience. Basic FeaturesSupport three translation modes including text translation voice translation and photo translation.The response speed is fast and accurate translation results appear immediately.Support to generate a new vocabulary book composed of words you don t understand.Built in dictionary of common words more than hundreds of common words in different languages.Widget function easy to master a new word every day. Whether you are a student or an office worker whether you want to learn a new language or improve efficiency you must not miss Daily Translator it will be your good helper to overcome language barriers and see a more exciting world!
